FBIS3-53744 "drnes012_n_94010" FBIS-NES-94-012 Document Type:Daily Report 19 Jan 1994 LEBANON Amal-Israel Clashes Occur in Southern Areas Israeli Shelling Continues NC1701203194 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 2000 GMT 17 Jan 94 NC1701203194 Beirut Radio Lebanon Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] News from the south indicates that the Israeli occupation forces continue to fire scores of illumination flares over Kafr Tibnit, Zawtar al-Sharqiyah, and Zawtar al-Gharbiyah Villages and the al-Litani River basin. Earlier the occupation forces fired scores of shells in the direction of valleys and hills adjacent to the al-Litani River basin. Reasons for the shelling were unknown.
